Create a Model from a Template

Quickly create a model using Einstein Discovery model templates. Each template provides a starter implementation for a common use case. To create:

In CRM Analytics Studio, click Create, then Model.
Select a template and click Continue.
Review summary information about the template.
Click Looks good, next if requirements are met.
Give your app a name and click Create.

Einstein Discovery creates an initial model with associated assets, including a dataset, dataflow, and documentation. Explore the initial model, insights, dataflow, and deployed model. Consider customizing to better reflect business requirements and goals.
